Note:
JavaScript Lexer - Complete tokenization for JavaScript/ECMAScript

Supports:
- All JavaScript keywords (ES6+)
- Operators (arithmetic, logical, bitwise, assignment, comparison)
- Literals (numbers, strings, template literals, regex, booleans, null, undefined)
- Arrow functions (=>)
- Spread/rest operator (...)
- Optional chaining (?.)
- Nullish coalescing (??)
- Comments (single-line, multi-line)
- Template literals with interpolation
- Regular expression literals

Token Types: 100+ distinct tokens for complete JavaScript support
:End Note

Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa" as Layout
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa" as StringCore

